---
import Page from '../../layouts/Page.astro';
import SectionBanner from '../../components/ui/SectionBanner.astro';
---

<Page
  title="Product Visualization"
  description="Product shots, configurators, exploded views, launch materials. Vision Graphics Kft. — Budapest-based studio, working globally since 1996."
>

  <SectionBanner
    image="/_img/banners/banner-product-viz.jpg"
    label="Speed Up Product Launch"
    title="Product Visualization"
    size="page"
    headingLevel="h1"
  />
  <div class="service-page">

    <div class="service-breadcrumb">
      <a href="/services/">Services</a>
      <span>→</span>
      <span>Product Visualization</span>
    </div>

    <p class="section-label">Service</p>
    <h2 class="display-lg service-h1">Product Visualization</h2>
    <p class="service-tagline-large">Market before you manufacture.</p>

    <div class="service-body-grid">
      <div class="service-main">

        <p class="service-lead">
          We blend 3D tech and AI to bring your products to life, from early concepts to
          market launch. Physical prototypes are expensive. Marketing teams need materials
          before production starts. We solve these challenges by combining high-end 3D
          visualization with smart AI tools.
        </p>

        <h2 class="service-section-h2">Why it matters</h2>
        <p class="body-text">
          3D visualization lets you produce campaign-quality imagery from CAD files alone —
          months before the first unit ships. Changes are easy; re-shoots are not.
          Our AI tools learn from each project, getting better at matching your brand's
          style over time.
        </p>
        <p class="body-text">
          We've produced product visuals for retail chains, consumer electronics, furniture,
          and industrial equipment. The workflow is the same; the level of technical accuracy varies.
        </p>

      </div>

      <aside class="service-sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-block">
          <h3 class="sidebar-label">What you need to start</h3>
          <ul class="sidebar-list">
            <li>CAD files or technical drawings</li>
            <li>Material / colour references</li>
            <li>Target use (print, web, video)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-block">
          <h3 class="sidebar-label">Pricing</h3>
          <p class="sidebar-price">from €3,000</p>
          <p class="sidebar-note">Depends on complexity and number of variants. Quote within one business day.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-cta">
          <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary sidebar-btn">Get a Quote</a>
          <a href="/portfolio/?cat=product-visualization" class="btn btn-ghost">See portfolio</a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>

  </div>

  <SectionBanner
    image="/_img/banners/banner-arch-viz.jpg"
    label="Product Design"
    title="Explore Before You Commit"
    headingLevel="h2"
  />
  <div class="service-section container">
    <p class="section-body">
      We turn your ideas into clear visuals before you spend money on prototypes. Our AI helps
      explore different designs quickly, while our 3D team makes sure everything looks exactly
      right. When you want to try something new, AI helps create the first draft, and our 3D
      artists fine-tune it until it's perfect.
    </p>
    <div class="deliverable-grid">
      {[
        {
          title: 'Test designs quickly',
          desc: 'Explore multiple options without full prototypes. See how different material, colour, and configuration choices look before committing to production.',
        },
        {
          title: 'Get feedback early',
          desc: 'Show stakeholders what you\'re planning at any stage of development — from rough concept to near-final design. Changes are easy while they\'re still cheap.',
        },
        {
          title: 'Make changes easily',
          desc: 'Update materials, colours, and configurations in hours. New versions are fast. When requirements shift, your visuals update with them.',
        },
      ].map(d => (
        <div class="deliverable-card">
          <h3 class="deliverable-title">{d.title}</h3>
          <p class="deliverable-desc">{d.desc}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>

  <SectionBanner
    image="/_img/banners/banner-general.jpg"
    label="Marketing & Sales"
    title="Launch-Ready Before Production"
    headingLevel="h2"
  />
  <div class="service-section container">
    <p class="section-body">
      Start your marketing earlier with high-quality visuals. Our AI tools help create consistent
      imagery across all your channels — from social media to trade shows. Because we work in 3D,
      we can show your product from any angle, in any setting, without expensive photo shoots.
    </p>
    <ul class="results-list">
      <li>Hero product shots for advertising and e-commerce</li>
      <li>Feature demonstration animations</li>
      <li>Campaign materials ready before units ship</li>
      <li>Interactive presentations for trade shows and pitches</li>
      <li>Exploded views showing assembly and key components</li>
      <li>Interactive 3D configurators for web — colour, material, and option variants</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <SectionBanner
    image="/_img/banners/banner-workflow.jpg"
    label="Technical Documentation"
    title="Complex Made Simple"
    headingLevel="h2"
  />
  <div class="service-section container">
    <p class="section-body">
      We make complex things clear with visual guides built from the same 3D data used for
      marketing. Our AI helps break down processes into clear steps, while our 3D team makes
      sure every detail is correct. When products change, we update everything quickly using
      the existing models.
    </p>
    <ul class="results-list">
      <li>Assembly instructions with step-by-step 3D views</li>
      <li>Maintenance procedure visualizations</li>
      <li>Interactive training materials for field teams</li>
      <li>Safety and emergency procedure visuals</li>
      <li>Technical documentation for manuals, tenders, and sales</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

</Page>

<style>
  .service-page {
    max-width: 1060px;
    padding-top: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
  }

  .service-breadcrumb {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-faint); margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .service-breadcrumb a { color: var(--color-text-muted); text-decoration: none; transition: color 200ms; }
  .service-breadcrumb a:hover { color: var(--color-accent); }

  .service-h1 { margin: 0.5rem 0 0.75rem; }
  .service-tagline-large { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--fs-h6); font-style: italic; color: var(--color-accent); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .service-lead { font-size: var(--fs-small); color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 65ch; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; }

  .service-body-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 240px; gap: 4rem; align-items: start; }
  .service-main { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }

  .service-section-h2 { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--fs-xs); font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-text-faint); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }

  /* Sub-sections */
  .service-section { padding-block: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); }

  .section-body { font-size: var(--fs-small); color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 65ch; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; }

  .deliverable-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: var(--color-border); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .deliverable-card { background: var(--color-surface); padding: 1.5rem; transition: background 200ms; }
  .deliverable-card:hover { background: var(--color-surface-2); }
  .deliverable-title { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--fs-small); font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .deliverable-desc { font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; max-width: none; }

  .results-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
  .results-list li { font-size: var(--fs-small); color: var(--color-text-muted); padding-left: 1.25rem; position: relative; line-height: 1.5; }
  .results-list li::before { content: '→'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--color-accent); font-size: var(--fs-xs); }

  .body-text { font-size: var(--fs-small); color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 65ch; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0; }

  /* Sidebar */
  .service-sidebar { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; position: sticky; top: 5rem; }
  .sidebar-block { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
  .sidebar-label { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--fs-xs); font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-text-faint); }
  .sidebar-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.35rem; }
  .sidebar-list li { font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: var(--color-text-muted); padding-left: 0.9rem; position: relative; }
  .sidebar-list li::before { content: '—'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--color-border); font-size: var(--fs-xs); }
  .sidebar-price { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--fs-h5); font-weight: 300; color: var(--color-text); margin: 0; }
  .sidebar-note { font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: var(--color-text-faint); line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; max-width: none; }
  .sidebar-cta { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
  .sidebar-btn { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .service-body-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .service-sidebar { position: static; }
    .deliverable-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
